		<item>
		<title>咳嗽怕吃什么水果和蔬菜（“咳嗽”最怕的2种水果）</title>
		<link>https://www.huacao77.com/12393.html</link>
					<comments>https://www.huacao77.com/12393.html#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[广少, 腹肌之广]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 05 Aug 2023 10:21:06 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[水果百科]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[放入]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[金桔]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[雪梨]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.huacao77.com/?p=12393</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[“咳嗽”最怕这2种水果，建议大家每天坚持吃1次，润喉止咳，清肺热，助力快转阴。 第一种：金桔 推荐食谱：雪梨炖 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/93b957d391ae471bed0ccb5a3f5940e4.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">“咳嗽”最怕这2种水果，建议大家每天坚持吃1次，润喉止咳，清肺热，助力快转阴。</span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">第一种：</span></span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">金桔</span></span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">推荐食谱：雪梨炖金桔</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">食材准备：金桔、雪梨、柠檬、黄冰糖、蜂蜜、食盐、小苏打</span></strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">详细步骤：</span></strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">1、准备500克金桔，放入1勺食盐，少许小苏打，倒入适量的清水，浸泡30分钟，去除农药残留，再徒手搓洗金桔，清洗干净后就完成了。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/cd1adb31e2d46ab0f02f229d374852ca.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">2、洗净后控干水分，用菜刀切掉两头，在上面切上十字花刀，煮的时候，营养成分更容易释放出来，每个金桔都要处理完，放旁边备用。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/8c9376d19dce0a738e366dbb6688bb28.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">3、再准备半个雪梨，清洗干净，切成小块，切好放入盆中，跟金桔放在一起，再来半个柠檬，从中间切开，搭配柠檬，营养元素更丰富。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/8b5f707028f2f0f06a64a8c3351e4b50.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">4、锅中加入1000毫升清水，放入30克黄冰糖，甜度根据个人口味选择，再放入金桔和雪梨，开大火烧开锅，开锅后转中火炖10分钟。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ece65d0065c863b79cf886be208fcb75.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">5、10分钟以后，转大火开始收汁，汤汁逐渐变粘稠，再烧2分钟，使汤汁都被金桔吸收，这个过程要不停搅拌，防止锅底会粘锅。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/139c4f5dfd45031a14e639277b3cb49c.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">6、汤汁变粘稠以后，关火稍微晾凉，挤入准备好的柠檬汁，柠檬汁要最后放，不然高温会破坏它的营养条件，最后再放一点蜂蜜，味道会更好喝。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/33e169daf980af1ee9d3bc100294225e.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">7、最后把金桔彻底放凉，装入玻璃罐中，或者保鲜盒中，盖上盖子，密封冷藏保存，放在外面容易潮湿发霉，所以一定要放入冰箱冷藏。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/7dd12030ccc9db4ee41e6e49c024b35c.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">8、吃的时候取两颗，放入杯子中，放入适量的开水，用来泡水喝，效果非常不错，可以缓解干咳，喉咙干痒，大家记得多喝它排毒。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/5df82ebfe38c5066f84af54bcaf22a70.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">第二种：</span></span><span style="color: green;"><span style="color: green;">雪梨</span></span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">推荐食谱：川贝炖雪梨</span></strong></span></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">食材准备：雪梨、枸杞、川贝、冰糖、矿泉水</span></strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">详细步骤：</span></strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">1、首先准备2个梨子，选择老一点的梨子，煮出来的口感更加甜，梨子的皮比较粗糙，会影响口感，所以要把皮削干净。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2fd279874ce47bcd566ebfd461d90acc.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">2、然后把梨子清洗干净，再用刀一分为四，再用刀去掉梨子的硬核，再切成大小均匀的小块，切好以后放入碗中备用。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/a93b3f8e0c2737cf6e8642a3c3e2b73b.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">3、另准备一个碗，放入少许的枸杞，把枸杞清洗干净，再准备38颗川贝，同样用清水清洗一下，沥干水分备用。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/224ac25ae503031349c68597df5a4dbf.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">4、准备一个洗干净的电炖锅，放入川贝、梨子，16颗冰糖，再加入适量的矿泉水，家里没有矿泉水，用自然水也可以。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/b6812d87d824c50f987a038070f56c62.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">5、盖上锅盖，把电动锅调成自动，慢慢地炖40分钟，时间到以后，加入泡好的枸杞，再煲两分钟，这锅雪梨汤就做好了。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/cda52650e57b830607df0db7f9e27c23.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">6、最后关火盛到碗中，清甜爽口，润肺又润喉，非常好喝，而且做法非常简单，喉咙干咳的人，抓紧时间买回家煮着喝吧。</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/e650efa80a17ba65bacfabcb482ca499.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>


</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
